A simple plugin to display icons along with posts/pages title. 


== Description ==

This is a simple plugin comes with a set of icons to display icons along with posts/pages title. You can change color/size of the icon. Easy to customize. 

== Installation ==

Extract the zip file and just drop the contents in the wp-content/plugins/ directory of your WordPress installation and then activate the Plugin from Plugins page. Add icons from metabox.
